<H1>Changing access permissions</H1>

<P>To change the access permissions for a file or
directory use the command</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>chmod <EM>mode filename</EM>
   chmod <EM>mode directory_name</EM></STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>The "mode" consists of three parts: <A HREF="change_perm1.html">who</A>
the permissions apply to, <A HREF="change_perm2.html">how</A>
the permissions are set and <A HREF="change_perm3.html">which</A>
permissions to set.</P>

